author: Amani Joseph
title: Amani Joseph
text:
i Will like to say this for the record, the service i received from this guy Name Lester made me realise these people work more than anyone in the company please if you have to chat on Live Support ask for this guys he is the best and fast and he will not leave you empty handed. Just try this guys you will be happy.
Congrat Lester and Please Keep it up and dont ever disappoint anyone. As for the company continue to make some improvement so that we can always enjoy the good service your Customer Care provide.
